Sharon Stone has taken to Instagram in a head-turning bikini selfie and her fans reacted to the post in a frenzy. The Basic Instinct star, 64, put on an age-defying display as she shared the image with her 3.3 million followers She wrote in the caption: “Why do I always get in shape when summers over?” The star was dressed in a multicoloured bikini as she beamed for a shot in her living room. American TV personality @CarsonKressley penned: “It’s never too late to be fabulous.” While actress @ChantelleDavey said: “I think you & that bikini need to head to Australia and we can sit by my pool (while you motivate me to get in shape like that)”